2. The 31st of December 2020 is specified as the different date for the 

purposes of section 110(6) of the Medical Practitioners Act 2007. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

29 July, 2020. 

STEPHEN DONNELLY, 
Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 4th August, 2020.

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This order specifies 31 December 2020 as the date on which a Section 110 
registration still in force shall cease to have effect.
